data.description: Sweet ranch style home with attached garage and large detached shop on 1 irrigated acre with 2 RV hookups and mature landscaping. Fall in love with the large covered porch as you step inside to a large living room area with another living area and dining room space as you approach the open concept kitchen. The large kitchen features tons of cabinet space and a pantry. There are three great sized bedrooms, with the primary bedroom being large with on-suite bathroom and step in shower. There is another full bathroom on this wing as well. If you step in from the south side of home you will enjoy the large laundry and mud room with half bath, and attached garage. For whatever your needs may be there is also a large detached shop with large air conditioner for summer months, and 2 RV hookups. You will love the maturely landscaped yard, huge garden area, and lots of fruit trees to enjoy. This property has an HOA for irrigation water, no other HOA or covenants. Come see this beauty today!
